🧠 Product: SignalStock (v1)

A swipe-based decision market where users earn from their signal

⸻

🎯 Core Idea (tight and executable)

A simple app where users:
	•	Compare two options (swipe left/right)
	•	Build a preference profile
	•	Earn Signal Shares based on how valuable their decisions are

Companies:
	•	Pay to access aggregated insights

Users:
	•	Get paid based on contribution quality

