⚙️ Scoring Algorithm (simple v1 version)

signal_score = (
    consistency_weight * consistency +
    uniqueness_weight * uniqueness +
    accuracy_weight * predictive_accuracy +
    engagement_weight * activity_level
)


⸻

💸 Payout Logic (v1 simple version)

user_payout = (
    user_signal_score / total_pool_score
) * dataset_revenue


